or short) is a library for building applications in a consistent"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and understandable way, with composition, testing, and ergonomics in mind. It can be used in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"SwiftUI, UIKit, and more, and on any Apple platform (iOS, macOS, tvOS, and watchOS)."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/composablearchitecture"}}}